Y IMAGES<br />\n圖像加註文字，<br />\n上一次木星和土星大合是近400年前，當時伽利略剛剛發明了望遠鏡。<br />\n<br />\n格林尼治皇家天文台的另一位天文學家布盧默說，木星和土星可能是天文愛好者的最佳觀測行星，因為它們明亮耀眼。<br />\n<br />\n所謂土星和木星大合是指兩顆星星如此接近，給人一種相互重疊，一起熠熠發光的假象。<br />\n布盧默解釋說，21日兩顆行星在夜空中如此接近，好像彼此重疊一樣。<br />\n<br />\n布盧默表示，對我們肉眼而言，土星與木星之間相距僅6.1角分（0.1度），但實際上木星距離地球有8億多公里，木星與土星之間的距離也差不多如此。<br />\n但最近幾個月，木星和土星這兩顆巨大的行星似乎越走越近，直到「相會」大合。這是一個不容錯過的天文現象。<br />\n<br />\n布盧默說，如果你有望遠鏡的話，甚至可以看到木星周圍的四大衛星。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-55215889.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.jp%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-55215889.amp&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Xs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=13c50bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.jp/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-55215889.amp</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"香港停英國航班再話英國肺炎"},{"pid":"72c3f083674b6c4e21d2554953cc704afd2d77fc","tid":2329811,"uid":201949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3e22446abd05a5486265d6cf6e9990c8f0301d9","tid":2329811,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abd0d51ca6c54a5bb7885ddaa1d01f24cdc950c2","tid":2329811,"uid":201949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31b40d137f319cadae4ee9e9dc11b64886f99a10","tid":2329811,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"發生左咩事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"天文景觀，木星土星大交合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"今晚車路士定韋斯咸"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"2:3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde3e580e0fb9afb7b4086e885707691474f7ce0","tid":2329811,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e224a47dfd7eb0a8f14a959f4974ecde96e79e90","tid":2329811,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{